## Module: Core - Crime

### Overview
This module covers key concepts in Core - Crime for the HSC legal course.

### Topics
- Topic 1 in Core - Crime
- Topic 2 in Core - Crime

### Learning Outcomes

Students will develop skills to:

- Identify and explain key concepts related to Core - Crime
- Analyse and interpret information related to Core - Crime
- Apply understanding of Core - Crime to solve problems
- Evaluate arguments and perspectives related to Core - Crime
- Communicate understanding of Core - Crime using appropriate terminology

### Key Concepts

This module introduces the following key concepts:

- Fundamental principles of Core - Crime
- Core terminology and definitions
- Theoretical frameworks
- Practical applications
- Critical analysis techniques

